{"tid":948712,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬向曼聯下戰書：我重拾100%","createTime":"2018-12-20T09:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T09:47:05.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21586c35a31325464129b53129f380e6807a1160","tid":948712,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=zyCA%2FeMUyPGN4KpnIxyjd%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=aa9cbd64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】巴黎聖日耳門球星尼馬強調已百分百痊癒，全力在歐聯16強撲擊剛易帥的曼聯，此說與下戰書無異。<br />\n<br />\n於2018年繁忙的賽程，尼馬（Neymar）可說多災多難，先在2月斷腳，僅僅趕及於夏天復出為巴西國家隊出戰世界盃，及至最近再次受創，因腹股溝傷患缺陣，但於早前歐聯已能披甲。<br />\n<br />\n「回到賽場，跟你的隊友並肩作戰永遠都是美好的事。受傷加上於世界盃失利，這個情況真的令人傷心，但你要從這些事情獲得啟發，重拾集中力，專注在新事情之上。」尼馬表示自己的狀態已回到100%。<br />\n<br />\nPSG於歐聯16強將鬥剛易帥的曼聯，尼馬坦言為這個抽籤結果高興：「這將是兩支偉大球隊的兩場偉大球賽。我們都知道曼聯所擁有的質素以及勝利心態。他們換了領隊，踢法不同，處於過渡期，但仍具質素。」"},{"pid":"913d5f6b04b1bade0b9bb6f976b2e1e68157891c","tid":948712,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"好睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f801c4d25950951b3a516693d30901b2fdc6ee","tid":948712,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:45:28.000Z","msg":"證明PSG開始驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb619dd942d4a7eb78a18e7ceffb93f0bb036490","tid":948712,"uid":4392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"你地成隊蒙住對眼黎踢都贏啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}